name: Santa María
description: There are legacies that no longer produce pride, an example of this is this building, it is not because of the building itself, it is because of its purpose since it is used for bullfights, a sick show where an animal is tortured for the satisfaction of a sick public, good news is that it is being used for other cultural purposes, but the best news is that this year there will be no bullfighting season since it is not profitable. little by little it progresses
